Subject: [PATCH] fix: correct submit flow and progress staleness

- QuickWizard handleSubmit: snapshot full step results BEFORE clearing
  entries, so anyFailed calculation is not reading an emptied map
- QuickWizard handleSubmit: await test-run cache invalidation before
  navigating so TestCaseSelector sees fresh data on arrival
- GuidedWizard: same await on test-run invalidation before navigate
- TestCaseSelector test-run + use-case queries: staleTime=0 so they
  always refetch on mount, not serve stale cache
- TesterScenarioPage test-run query: staleTime=0 for same reason
